                    </div>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Hogar Combinado</h3>
                    <p class="card-desc">Tu refugio, protegido contra todo.</p>
                </div>
                <ul class="feature-list">
                    <li>
                        <svg class="check-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
                        <span>Incendio y Robo contenido</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <svg class="check-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
                        <span>Electrodomésticos</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <svg class="check-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
                        <span>Urgencias 24hs (Plomería/Gas)</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#" class="btn-card">Cotizar Casa</a>
            </div>

            <div class="card-pro featured">
                <div class="badge-popular">MÁS ELEGIDO</div>
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="icon-circle" style="background: var(--primary); color: white; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(var(--primary-rgb), 0.3);">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 16H9m10 0h3v-3.15a1 1 0 0 0-.84-.99L16 11l-2.7-3.6a1 1 0 0 0-.8-.4H5.24a2 2 0 0 0-1.8 1.1l-.8 1.63A6 6 0 0 0 2 12a6 6 0 0 0 6 6h7a6 6 0 0 0 6-6c0-1.5-.7-2.9-2-4z"/><circle cx="7" cy="17" r="2"/><circle cx="17" cy="17" r="2"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Automotor</h3>
                    <p class="card-desc">Manejá tranquilo, nosotros respondemos.</p>
                </div>
                <ul class="feature-list">
                    <li>
                        <svg class="check-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
                        <span><strong>Todo Riesgo</strong> con Franquicia</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <svg class="check-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
                        <span>Granizo e Inundación</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <svg class="check-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
                        <span>Auxilio Mecánico Premium</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <svg class="check-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
                        <span>Gestión de reclamos incluida</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#" class="btn-card btn-primary-card">Cotizar Auto Ahora</a>
            </div>

            <div class="card-pro">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <div class="icon-circle" style="background: #fff7ed; color: #ea580c;">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Vida & Accidentes</h3>
                    <p class="card-desc">Respaldo financiero para lo que importa.</p>
                </div>
                <ul class="feature-list">
                    <li>
                        <svg class="check-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
                        <span>Seguro de Vida Individual</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <svg class="check-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
                        <span>Accidentes Personales (AP)</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <svg class="check-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>
                        <span>Cobertura 24hs / Laboral</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <a href="#" class="btn-card">Consultar</a>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* GRID LAYOUT */
    .cards-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        align-items: center; /* Para que la destacada pueda crecer verticalmente */
    }

    /* TARJETA BASE */
    .card-pro {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 2.5rem;
        border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .card-pro:hover {
        transform: translateY(-8px);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border-color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    /* TARJETA DESTACADA (Auto) */
    .card-pro.featured {
        border: 2px solid var(--primary);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(var(--primary-rgb), 0.15);
        transform: scale(1.05);
        z-index: 2;
    }
    
    .card-pro.featured:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05) translateY(-8px);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .card-pro.featured { transform: scale(1); }
        .card-pro.featured:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); }
    }

    /* ETIQUETA POPULAR */
    .badge-popular {
        position: absolute;
        top: -12px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        background: var(--primary);
        color: white;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        padding: 4px 12px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    /* CABECERA TARJETA */
    .icon-circle {
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .card-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: #1e293b;
    }

    .card-desc {
        color: #64748b;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* LISTA DE BENEFICIOS */
    .feature-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0 0 2.5rem 0;
        flex-grow: 1; /* Empuja el botón al fondo */
    }

    .feature-list li {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #334155;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .check-icon {
        width: 20px;
        height: 20px;
        stroke: var(--primary); /* O color verde éxito */
        stroke-width: 3;
        fill: none;
        stroke-linecap: round;
        stroke-linejoin: round;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    /* BOTONES */
    .btn-card {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 12px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        background: #f1f5f9;
        color: #475569;
        transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-card:hover {
        background: #e2e8f0;
        color: #1e293b;
    }

    .btn-primary-card {
        background: var(--primary);
        color: white;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(var(--primary-rgb), 0.3);
    }

    .btn-primary-card:hover {
        background: var(--primary-dark, #2563eb); /* Asegúrate de tener un color oscuro o usa filter */
        filter: brightness(0.9);
        color: white;
    }
</style>